@c.shu Can you confirm that you are using standard 1/8" wall 2x1 tube (REV-21-3555 or similar) and not the Rev MAXTube 2x1 (REV-21-2590) or 2x1 Light (REV-21-2289)? If so, then the below manufacturers have an equivalent part number in stock (there may be others as well).

  • West Coast Products: WCP-0374
  • The Thrifty Bot: TTB-0260

@Greg_Needel FYI, on the Endcaps page, these part numbers have the wrong Onshape document linked:

  • REV-21-3610
  • REV-21-3611
  • REV-21-3612
  • REV-21-3613
  • REV-21-3616
